<h2>Summary</h2>
Whatâ€™s more important than what your skills gaps are is how you deal with them. Consulting with your team as a whole and one-on-one can give you vital insight into where their skills gaps are, how they affect the teamâ€™s work, and what might be the best way to fill them.&nbsp;

Upskilling, hiring, and outsourcing to fill skills gaps each have their own potential advantages and disadvantages, which you should weigh up with your teamâ€™s input before deciding which solution would work best for you.

